name: com.realmai.unity
description:
Unity package for REALM_AI project. This package is created for a research project and is provided "as is".

This package adds the prefab "Realm AI Module", which is design to provide a simple integration of ML-Agents for 2D platformer games and to collect data while training for generating insights afterwards.
Documentation and setup guide can be found https://realm-ai-project.github.io/documentation/
